nodes.text: The Battle for Theed! was a Star Wars Insider article that showed never-before-seen storyboards drawn by Edwin Natividad for Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace, depicting Jedi Master Qui-Gon Jinn and his Padawan, Obi-Wan Kenobi, fighting against the Trade Federation's B1-Series battle droids and droidekas, shortly before getting into the Theed Hangar. This article appeared in Star Wars Insider 131.
